{"version":3,"term":{"cols":0,"rows":0,"type":"xterm-256color"},"timestamp":1775662598,"command":"bash -c \"\n  bash ~/halo-ai-core/install.sh --yes-all\n  echo\n  echo ══════════════════════════════════════\n  echo    BENCHMARKS — Out of the Box\n  echo ══════════════════════════════════════\n  echo\n  echo Downloading Qwen3-30B-A3B Q4_K_M...\n  mkdir -p ~/models\n  curl -sL -o ~/models/Qwen3-30B-A3B-Q4_K_M.gguf https://huggingface.co/unsloth/Qwen3-30B-A3B-GGUF/resolve/main/Qwen3-30B-A3B-Q4_K_M.gguf\n  echo Model ready — running benchmarks...\n  source /etc/profile.d/rocm.sh\n  llama-bench -m ~/models/Qwen3-30B-A3B-Q4_K_M.gguf -ngl 99 -p 512 -n 128\n  echo\n  echo Done. These are your out-of-the-box numbers.\n\"","env":{"SHELL":"/usr/bin/bash"}}
